    "bio": "Business Automation Expert | n8n & AI Integrator I help companies streamline operations and eliminate manual busywork. I design and build custom automation workflows that connect your apps, data, and teams. My goal is to turn chaotic processes into reliable systems, allowing you to focus on strategy while the software handles the routine. Specialization: Process Optimization, CRM Integrations, AI Agents, and Custom Backend Logic.",
